data.enText: a person whose job is to connect, repair, etc. electrical equipment

simple_means.memory_skill: electr 电的 + ician 人（精于某种学术或从事某种职业）→ 电工

tr: a person who installs or repairs electrical or telephone lines

value.def: An electrician is a person whose job is to install and repair electrical equipment.

Egypt 埃及 + ian …国的；…地方的，某人的或某宗教的 → 埃及（人）的
